# Copy this file to frontend/.env (local dev) and set the equivalent in
# Vercel's project settings for production — see SUPABASE_MIGRATION.md.
#
# There is no VITE_SUPABASE_URL / VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY here on purpose:
# the frontend never talks to Supabase directly. Every read and write goes
# through the FastAPI backend, which is the only thing holding a Supabase
# key (the service role key, server-side only). This keeps the same
# architecture you already have (frontend -> FastAPI -> data) and means no
# Supabase credential of any kind is ever shipped to the browser.

# Your deployed backend URL (Render), or http://127.0.0.1:8000 for local dev.
VITE_API_BASE=http://127.0.0.1:8000
